    {
      "id": "f1275802_36c96e80",
      "file_path": "packages/docker/src/main/docker/Dockerfile",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 23,
      "message": "I think in Debian/Ubuntu lower case http_proxy is the one honored by the OS.   I don't think we need the upper case version.  The format honored by the OS is:\n\nexport http_proxy=http://<username>:<password>@<proxy-server>:<proxy-port>",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 477,
        "name": "Jorge Hernandez",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "jorge.hernandez-herrero@att.com",
        "username": "jhh"
      },
      "updated": "2020-01-29 17:15:08.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "id": "5f03d139_ab58f7b5",
      "file_path": "packages/install/src/files/base.conf",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 42,
      "message": "I think we could remove the upper case version .. and we probably should leave them commented out, ie., it would be just an indication for the installer on what to change if they want to use a proxy, ie.\n\n#http_proxy=\n#https_proxy=",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 477,
        "name": "Jorge Hernandez",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "jorge.hernandez-herrero@att.com",
        "username": "jhh"
      },
      "updated": "2020-01-29 17:15:08.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "id": "bfd392b0_415b8bf3",
      "file_path": "packages/install/src/files/base.conf",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 67,
      "message": "I think we can leave these commented out as well, we want to indicate the installer what variables to change to override current \"onap nexus\" repos.   As an example you could place the actual onap nexus urls that were replaced,\nie.\n\n# MVN_SNAPSHOT_REPO_URL=http..onap..nexus..release\n# MVN_RELEASE_REPO_URL=http..onap..nexus..snapshot",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 477,
        "name": "Jorge Hernandez",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "jorge.hernandez-herrero@att.com",
        "username": "jhh"
      },
      "updated": "2020-01-29 17:15:08.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
