      "message": "oh ok, in my set up things seem to work ok with all the tooling with http_proxy and https_proxy lower case set up.   In any case, if you don't need the HTTPS one for your CI toolchain, you could leave them commented out.   In a regular lab install, the user could always go to the base.conf and set them up so they are avaiable at runtime at container initialization if they need to.",
